OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773925870
OL,3,CNorthumberland masseur in court
OL,4,Ccharged with 55 sexual offences
OL,6,FA masseur has appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with 55 sexual offences
OL,8,Frelating to 14 women.
OL,10,FTerence McBrien, 72, from Alnwick,
OL,11,FNorthumberland, appeared before
OL,12,FBerwick Magistrates' Court on Thursday
OL,13,Ffor a brief hearing.
OL,15,FHe faces 55 offences, comprising one
OL,16,Fcount of attempted rape, seven counts
OL,17,Fof sexual assault by penetration, 34
OL,18,Fcounts of sexual assault by touching,
OL,19,Fand 13 counts of voyeurism.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
