OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773925870
OL,3,CNorthumberland masseur in court
OL,4,Ccharged with 55 sexual offences
OL,6,FThe charges relate to 14 women,
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police has previously
OL,8,Fsaid, and the allegations date between
OL,9,F2011 and 2021.
OL,11,FMcBrien, who represented himself,
OL,12,Fwalked past photographers and TV
OL,13,Fcameras outside court, wearing a tweed
OL,14,Fcap, jacket and tie. He did not enter
OL,15,Fpleas during the hearing, which lasted
OL,16,Fless than ten minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
