OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773925870
OL,3,CNorthumberland masseur in court
OL,4,Ccharged with 55 sexual offences
OL,6,FHe spoke in a clear voice to confirm
OL,7,Fhis name, date of birth and address,
OL,8,Fand said: "Fully understood ma'am"
OL,9,Fwhen Chairman of the Bench, Wendy
OL,10,FBrett, told him he was being granted
OL,11,Fconditional bail.
OL,13,FShe told him he must next appear at
OL,14,FNewcastle Crown Court on 16 April for
OL,15,Fa plea hearing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
